# Branch discipline

Check `git branch --show-current` before editing.

## Install (all branches on current `main`)

```bash
npm install   # once at repo root — never per-app npm install for workspace members
```

Workspace members: `dashboard-product`, `tracebud-marketing`, `tracebud-offline`, `field-auth`, `tracebud-backend`.

## Branch scope

| Branch | Purpose |
| --- | --- |
| `main` | Deployable baseline |
| `feature/*` | Product slices (offline, dashboard, backend, etc.) |
| `chore/*` | Repo maintenance only (CI, workspaces, docs) |

Do not mix repo restructuring with product features in one PR.

## Root files — touch only for repo maintenance

- Root `package.json`, `package-lock.json`, `turbo.json`
- `.github/workflows/ci.yml`
- `docs/repo-branches.md`, `docs/vercel-monorepo.md`

Product code lives under `apps/*` and `tracebud-backend/`.

## Rollback

Tag `pre-workspaces-2026-06-20` = last commit before npm workspaces adoption.
